    Vector: [RELATION]
    Pressure: Yuki's birthday in 2 weeks, 6 days. She doesn't know if she can call. She doesn't know if she deserves to.
    Success: Anchor helps her walk through that door too. She touched his arm. The door is still closed, but it's no longer locked.
    Failure: She stays on this side, forever wondering.

